MediaCast,is,a,digital,signage,customization,and,organization,system,for,companies,with,a,network,of,digital,signs,The,software,as,a,service,offering,helps,simplify,and,automate,point,of,sale,point,of,wait,or,point,of,transit,communications,networks,The,Mediacast,API,allows,users,of,the,software,with,programming,capabilities,to,integrate,the,new,management,software,into,their,existing,systems,to,avoid,retraining,employees,The,Mediacast,API,also,allows,companies,to,overlay,their,own,rules,of,how,content,behaves,within,the,system,to,coincide,with,their,preexisting,business,practices,Full,documentation,is,available,upon,request